(also unusual vendors and trade-in spells)<br>
Most other spells can be found at the shaman guildhalls in Halas, Ogguk, Grobb and Cabalis as well as the Barbarian Hut in Firiona Vie, the "poison-vendors" in Innothule Swamp and Everfrost Peaks, the gypsy "sight and vision/inviso spells" vendor at the Gypsy Camp in Oasis of Marr, and the female barbarian "wolf pet" vendor standing near the water at the Barbarian village in the Western Plains of Karana.<br>
<br>
Level 34:<br>
<br>
Shock of the Tainted - vendor-purchased at pirate camp near docks in Icelclad<br>
<br>
Level 39:<br>
<br>
Tumultuous Strength - Iceclad/Garou; Skyshrine/Suez (drakes); Great Divide/Guardian Wurms, Tower of Frozen Shadow in Iceclad (Second Floor off Librarian Assistant, Third Floor off Armored Shadow, Fourth and Fifth Floors off most any mob), Ulthork Man 'O War in Eastern Wastes, Sifaye Thanes in Wakening Lands, Ry'Gorr Fort in Eastern Wastes<br>
<br>
Level 44:<br>
<br>
Blast of Poison - Great Divide/Guardian Wurms, Icewell Keep Sentinels & Watchers<br>
<br>
Summon Companion - vendor-purchased in smuggler's area of East Commonlands tunnel<br>
<br>
Level 49:<br>
<br>
none noted<br>
<br>
Level 50:<br>
<br>
Spirit Quickening - Crystalline ShadowWurms in Great Divide, the wurm Shardtooth, Icewell Keep Sentinels & Watchers/Avalanche Golem/Loremaster; Plane of Growth off various mobs, Skyshrine off the "deeper" wyverns, Velektor's Labarinth off various kobolds<br>
<br>
Level 51:<br>
<br>
Talisman of Jasinth - Sebilis/Dars and Jins; Chardok/reg mobs <br>
<br>
Level 52:<br>
<br>
Insidious Decay - "TRADE IN QUEST"<br>
In both Firiona Vie (barb hut) and Overthere, there is a person you can turn in these 4 spells to:<br>
<br>
Talisman of Jasinth (level 51)<br>
Spirit of Scale (level 52)<br>
Cripple (level 53)<br>
Cannabalize III (level 54)<br>
<br>
When you turn them in (one at a time mind you) you will get one of these 4 spells randomly (no way to predict which you get.<br>
Insidious Decay (level 52)<br>
Talisman of Shadoo (level 53)<br>
Shroud of the Spirits (level 54)<br>
